ally%20from%20Bihar's%20Samastipur%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20his%20Bengaluru%20flat%20on%20Monday.%20Police%20found%20a%20detailed%20note%20at%20his%20home%2C%20with%20every%20page%20starting%20with%20%26quot%3Bjustice%20is%20due%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20suicide%20note%20and%20video%2C%20Subhash%20alleged%20that%20he%20married%20Nikita%20in%202019%20after%20finding%20her%20on%20a%20matchmaking%20website.%20The%20couple%20had%20a%20son%20the%20next%20year.%20He%20alleged%20that%20Nikita%20and%20her%20family%20would%20ask%20him%20for%20huge%20amounts%20of%20money%20to%20set%20up%20businesses.%20Arguments%20broke%20out%20when%20he%20refused%20and%20she%20eventually%20left%20home%20in%202021%20with%20their%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20Atul%20alleged%2C%20she%20filed%20a%20litany%20of%20cases%20against%20him%20and%20his%20family%20members%20under%20serious%20charges%20of%20cruelty%20against%20a%20woman%2C%20dowry%20harassment%20and%20even%20murder.%20The%20Singhanias%20accused%20Atul%20and%20his%20family%20members%20of%20harassing%20Nikita's%20late%20father%20for%20dowry%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20death.%20This%20case%20was%2C%20however%2C%20later%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%20said%20before%20his%20death%20that%20Nikita%20and%20her%20family%20members%20had%20filed%20multiple%20cases%20to%20harass%20him%20and%20extort%20a%20huge%20sum%20as%20alimony%20and%20maintenance.%20He%20said%20Nikita%20had%20demanded%20Rs%203%20crore%20to%20settle%20the%20case.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20court%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20pay%20Rs%2080%2C000%20monthly%20as%20maintenance%20to%20Nikita%20and%20his%20son%2C%20but%20she%20wanted%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20targeting%20the%20judicial%20system%20of%20favouring%20women%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20Subhash%20wrote%20in%20the%20note%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20I%20work%20hard%20and%20become%20better%20at%20my%20work%2C%20the%20more%20I%20and%20my%20family%20will%20be%20ha