%20all%20came%20here%20together%20and%20decided%20to%20reopen%20the%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20Mishra%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20temple%20had%20been%20closed%20for%20decades%20and%20the%20local%20residents%20confirmed%20it%20had%20been%20locked%20since%201978.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20also%20has%20a%20well%20nearby%20which%20the%20authorities%20plan%20to%20reopen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeeks%20after%20four%20people%20died%20in%20a%20violence%20over%20a%20court-ordered%20survey%20of%20the%20Shahi%20Jama%20Masjid%20in%20this%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20district%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20launched%20a%20campaign%20to%20tackle%20encroachments%20and%20power%20theft%20in%20areas%20around%20the%20Mughal-era%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20residents%20shared%20their%20memories%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20with%20many%20highlighting%20its%20importance%20as%20a%20religious%20site%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%2C%20located%20in%20Khaggu%20Sarai%20is%20just%20over%20a%20kilometre%20away%20from%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20which%20is%20situated%20in%20Kot%20Garvi%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20Rastogi%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kot%20Garvi%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20heard%20a%20lot%20about%20this%20temple%20from%20our%20ancestors.%20It%20is%20an%20ancient%20temple%20but%20it%20was%20closed%20long%20ago%20because%20people%20only%20a%20particular%20community%20lived%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20heard%20that%20this%20temple%20must%20be%20at%20least%20500%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishnu%20Shankar%20Rastogi%2C%2082-year-old%20patron%20of%20the%20Nagar%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%2C%20shared%20his%20personal%20connection%20with%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20lived%20in%20Khaggu%20Sarai%20since%20my%20birth.%20After%20the%201978%20riots%2C%20our%20community%20was%20forced%20to%20migrate%20from%20the%20area.%20This%20temple%2C%20dedicated%20to%20our%20Kulguru%2C%20has%20been%20locked%20since%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Rastogi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAround%2025-30%20Hindu%20families%2C%20including%20ours%2C%20used%20to%20live%20in%20the%20Khaggu%20Sarai%20area.%20After%20the%201978%20riots%2C%20we%20sold%20our%20house%20and%20left%20this%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Rastogi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20is%20an%20ancient%20temple%20and%20was%20known%20as%20Bhasma%20Shankar%20temple.%20It%20was%20called%20the%20temple%20of%20the%20Rastogi%20community%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20the%20people%20of%20our%20community%20used%20to%20come%20here%20for%20worship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Sankhydhar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Sambhal%2C%20said%20he%20has%20heard%20a%20lot%20about%20this%20temple.%20%26quot%3BPeople's%20sorrows%20were%20relieved%20by%20visiting%20here.%20But%20it%20was%20closed%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Now%20the%20people%20here%20will%20visit%20again%20and%20earn%20the%20benefits%20of%20virtue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20Sambhal%20on%20November%2024%20over%20surveying%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20Shahi%20Jama%20Masjid.%20Four%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20several%2C%20including%20police%20personnel%2C%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20imam%20of%20another%20mosque%20in%20Sambhal%20was%20on%20Friday%20fined%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20allegedly%20using%20a%20loudspeaker%20at%20high%20volume%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Anar%20Wali%20Masjid%20in%20the%20Kot%20Garvi%20area%2C%20according%20to%20administration%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20imam%20was%20directed%20to%20refrain%20from%20similar%20conduct%20for%20the%20next%20six%20months%2C%20according%20to%20an%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20SDM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20N