com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-australia%2Frishabh-pant-marks-gabba-return-with-a-wicketkeeping-milestone-watch%2Farticleshow%2F116330099.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Nehru%20Model%20Failed%2C%20We're%20Trying%20To%20Correct%20It%20Since%202014'%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20'Nehru%20development%20model'%2C%20inevitably%20produced%20a%20'Nehru%20foreign%20policy'%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe%20seek%20to%20correct%20that%20abroad%26quot%3B%2C%20just%20as%20efforts%20being%20made%20to%20%26quot%3Breform%26quot%3B%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20model%20at%20home%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20(EAM)%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20virtual%20address%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20book%20'The%20Nehru%20Development%20Model'%20by%20former%20NITI%20Aayog%20vice%20chairman%20Arvind%20Panagariya%2C%20he%20also%20said%20the%20author%20suggests%20that%20former%20prime%20minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20choices%20set%20India%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeterministic%20path%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20model%20and%20its%20accompanying%20narrative%20permeated%20our%20politics%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20planning%20system%2C%20the%20judiciary%2C%20the%20public%20space%2C%20including%20the%20media%2C%20and%20most%20of%20all%20teaching%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20both%20Russia%20and%20China%20today%20%26quot%3Bunambiguously%20reject%26quot%3B%20the%20economic%20assumptions%20of%20that%20period%2C%20which%20they%20did%20more%20than%20anyone%20else%20to%20propagate.%20Yet%2C%20these%20very%20beliefs%20%26quot%3Bappear%20to%20live%20on%26quot%3B%20in%20influential%20sections%20of%20our%20country%20even%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertainly%20after%202014%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20vigorous%20effort%20towards%20course%20correction%2C%20but%20the%20author%20does%20assert%20with%20good%20reasons%20that%20it%20still%20remains%20an%20uphill%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%2C%20the%20minister%20further%20said%20%26quot%3BA%20Nehru%20development%20model%20inevitably%20produced%20a%20Nehru%20foreign%20policy.%20We%20seek%20to%20correct%20that%20abroad%2C%20just%20as%20we%20try%20to%20reform%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20model%20at%20home.%26quot%3B%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bresistance%26quot%3B%20to%20one%20is%20based%20on%20an%20%26quot%3Battachment%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20other%2C%20Jaishankar%20argued%20and%20said%20the%20two%20need%20to%20tackled%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bintegral%20whole%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20his%20address%20by%20quoting%20a%20famous%20line%20by%20an%20American%20policymaker%20on%20India's%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201947%2C%20John%20Foster%20Dulles%20famously%20declared%2C%20I%20quote%2C%20'In%20India%2C%20Soviet%20Communism%20exercises%20a%20strong%20influence%20through%20the%20interim%20Hindu%20government'.%20He%20of%20course%2C%20could%20not%20have%20been%20more%20wrong%20about%20ascribing%20that%20adjective%20to%20the%20then%20government.%20But%2C%20more%20relevant%2C%20this%20was%20an%20assertion%20that%20for%20decades%20was%20treated%20as%20a%20geopolitical%20over-reaction%20of%20American%20policy%20makers%20to%20an%20independent%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EAM%20said%20that%20over%20these%20years%2C%20he%20has%20often%20asked%20himself%20whether%20Dulles%20was%20altogether%20wrong%20on%20this%20matter.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20in%20Prof%20Panagariya's%20book%2C%20I%20found%20a%20substantial%20answer%20to%20that%20concern.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWe%20all%20know%20that%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20ideological%20drive%20to%20advance%20a%20particular%20economic%20model%20for%20an%20India%20that%20has%20just%20gained%20freedom.%20The%20belief%20that%20was%20propagated%20was%20modulated%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20but%20never%20fundamentally%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20root%20cause%20was%20an%20analysis%20that%20the%20only%20counter%20to%20imperialism%20lay%20in%20socialism%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20in%20general%20terms%2C%20but%20one%20particular%20paradigm%20that%20was%20centred%20around%20heavy%20industries.%20For%20that%20reason%2C%20the%20author%20actually%20characterised%20it%20as%20a%20'Nehru%20Development%20Model'%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20in%20his%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paradox%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20now%2C%20there's%20actually%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20consensus%20that%20this%20development%20model%20eventually%20failed%20the%20country%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Breluctance%20to%20confidently%20explore%20alternatives%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20we%20end%20up%20doing%20the%20reforms%20we%20must%2C%20rarely%20the%20reforms%20we%20should%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EAM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20underlined%20there%20is%20no%20question%20that%20India%20has%20benefited%20from%20greater%20openness%20in%20the%20last%2033%20years.%20But%2C%20the%20situation%20today%20is%20very%20much%20%26quot%3Bmore%20complex%26quot%3B%20than%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20live%20in%20an%20era%20of%20weaponised%20economics%2C%20one%20that%20throws%20up%20question%20as%20to%20what%20exactly%20we%20are%20exposing%20abroad%20and%20to%20whom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20concepts%20today%20are%20therefore%20less%20of%20openness%20and%20more%20of%20resiliency%2C%20reliability%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20even%20say%2C%20of%20trust%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20EAM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenness%20with%20caution%20is%20perhaps%20a%20recommended%20approach%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Atmanirbharta%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsynonym%20for%20protectionism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20actually%20a%20call%20to%20think%20and%20to%20act%20for%20ourselves%2C%20as%20much%20as%20it%20is%20to%20ensure%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734230040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fi4vj5dq_-jaishankar_650x400_07_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnehru-model-failed-were-trying-to-correct-it-since-2014-s-jaishankar-7251347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20'Nehru%20development%20model'%2C%20inevitably%20produced%20a%20'Nehru%20foreign%20policy'%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe%20seek%20to%20correct%20that%20abroad%26quot%3B%2C%20just%20as%20efforts%20being%20made%20to%20%26quot%3Breform%26quot%3B%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20model%20at%20home%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20(EAM)%20S%20Jaishankar%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnehru-model-failed-were-trying-to-correct-it-since-2014-s-jaishankar-7251347%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20President-elect%20Trump%20picks%20loyalist%20Richard%20Grenell%20for%20special%20missions%20envoy%20post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734230035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116330040%2Cimgsize-605244.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-president-elect-trump-picks-loyalist-richard-grenell-for-special-missions-envoy-post%2Farticleshow%2F116329821.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2