es%20from%20August%205%20to%20October%2022%2C%20Alam%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20a%20spate%20of%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20attacks%20on%20temples%20in%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20that%20triggered%20strong%20concerns%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20the%20United%20States%20will%20hold%20the%20Bangladeshi%20interim%20government%20accountable%20for%20ensuring%20the%20protection%20of%20religious%20and%20ethnic%20minorities%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Centre%20for%20Democracy%2C%20Pluralism%20and%20Human%20Rights%20(CDPHR)%20on%20Friday%20there%20were%20190%20reported%20cases%20of%20looting%2C%2032%20homes%20were%20set%20on%20fire%2C%2016%20temples%20were%20desecrated%20and%20two%20incidents%20of%20sexual%20violence%20were%20recorded%20between%20August%205%20and%209%20after%20Hasina's%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CDPHR%20released%20a%20report%20titled%20'Bangladesh%20Minorities%20Under%20Siege%3A%20A%20Wake-Up%20Call%20for%20the%20International%20Community'%20on%20the%20state%20of%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20details%20the%20incidents%20of%20violence%20and%20unrest%20affecting%20the%20Hindu%20communities%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20political%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20August%2020%2C%20the%20number%20of%20reported%20incidents%20had%20increased%20significantly%2C%20with%202%2C010%20total%20cases%20of%20violence%20against%20the%20Hindus%2C%20including%20the%20desecration%20of%2069%20temples%20and%20attacks%20on%20157%20families%2C%20it%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20s