did%20not%20provide%20further%20details%2C%20Spanish%20media%20reports%20said%20the%2071-year-old%20died%20after%20falling%20down%20a%20ravine%20while%20hiking%20in%20the%20mountains%20near%20Barcelona%20with%20several%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20with%20deep%20regret%20that%20we%20announce%20the%20unexpected%20death%20of%20Isak%20Andic%2C%20our%20non-executive%20chairman%20and%20founder%20of%20Mango%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Barcelona-based%20company's%20CEO%2C%20Toni%20Ruiz%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsak%20has%20been%20an%20example%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20He%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20Mango%2C%20leaving%20an%20indelible%20mark%20thanks%20to%20his%20strategic%20vision%2C%20his%20inspiring%20leadership%20and%20his%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20values%20that%20he%20himself%20imbued%20in%20our%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchez%20wrote%20on%20social%20network%20X%20that%20Andic%20had%20%26quot%3Bturned%20this%20Spanish%20firm%20into%20a%20world%20leader%20in%20fashion%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20work%20and%20entrepreneurial%20vision%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20head%20of%20Catalonia's%20regional%20government%2C%20Salvador%20Illa%2C%20hailed%20Andic%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20committed%20businessman%20who%2C%20with%20his%20leadership%2C%20has%20contributed%20to%20making%20Catalonia%20great%20and%20projecting%20it%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20leaves%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20the%20Catalan%20and%20global%20fashion%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20in%20a%20post%20of%20social%20network%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EColour%20and%20style%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media-shy%20entrepreneur%20was%20one%20of%20Spain's%20richest%20men.%20Forbes%20estimates%20he%20and%20his%20family%20have%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%244.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20his%20watch%2C%20to%20help%20boost%20sales%20the%20company%20hired%20big%20stars%20such%20as%20British%20model%20Kate%20Moss%2C%20Spanish%20actor%20Penelope%20Cruz%2C%20and%20French%20footballer%20Antoine%20Griezmann%20for%20its%20marketing%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20legacy%20reflects%20the%20achievements%20of%20a%20business%20project%20marked%20by%20success%2C%20and%20also%20by%20his%20human%20quality%2C%20his%20proximity%20and%20the%20care%20and%20affection%20that%20he%20always%20had%20and%20at%20all%20times%20conveyed%20to%20the%20entire%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20Ruiz%20said%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bhis%20departure%20leaves%20a%20huge%20void%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201953%20in%20Istanbul%2C%20Andic%20moved%20to%20Barcelona%20in%20Spain's%20wealthy%20northeastern%20Catalonia%20region%20with%20his%20family%20when%20he%20was%2014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20opened%20his%20first%20shop%20on%20the%20Paseo%20de%20Gracia%2C%20Barcelona's%20famous%20shopping%20street%20in%201984%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20older%20brother%20Nahman.%20It%20was%20hugely%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpain%20had%20just%20emerged%20from%20a%20decades-long%20dictatorship%20that%20ended%20with%20the%20death%20of%20General%20Francisco%20Franco%20in%201975%2C%20and%20consumers%20were%20hungry%20for%20more%20modern%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20saw%20that%20we%20needed%20colour%2C%20style%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20global%20retail%20director%2C%20Cesar%20de%20Vicente%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20AFP%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20name%2C%20one%20brand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndic%20quickly%20opened%20dozens%20of%20more%20stores%20in%20Spain%20and%20then%20abroad%2C%20starting%20in%20neighbouring%20Portugal%20and%20France%2C%20all%20under%20the%20name%20Mango.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20%26quot%3Brealised%20that%20having%20the%20same%20name%2C%20having%20the%20same%20brand%20in%20all%20the%20shops%2C%20would%20make%20the%20concept%20much%20stronger%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20De%20Vicente.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20versatile%20offerings%2C%20which%20encompasses%20both%20professional%20and%20casual%20styles%2C%20have%20been%20a%20hit%20with%20consumers%2C%20with%20Mango%20selling%20nearly%20160%20million%20items%20of%20clothing%20and%20accessories%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20consolidated%20its%20position%20as%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20international%20fashion%20groups%2C%20with%20a%20major%20presence%20in%20more%20than%20120%20markets%20and%2015%2C500%20employees%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retailer%20closed%202023%20with%20a%20turnover%20of%203.1%20billion%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20its%20main%20domestic%20rival%20Inditex%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20fashion%20retailer%20and%20owner%20of%20the%20popular%20Zara%20brand%2C%20%C2%A0Mango%20strives%20to%20quickly%20adjust%20its%20production%20to%20the%20latest%20fashion%20trends%20while%20offering%20affordable%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMango%20does%20not%20own%20any%20factory%2C%20outsourcing%20its%20production%20mainly%20to%20lower-cost%20Turkey%20and%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20latests%20strategic%20plan%2C%20Mango%20aims%20to%20have%20more%20than%203%2C000%20stores%20worldwide%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734226740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ffqavio6o_isak-andic_625x300_14_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisak-andic-founder-of-mango-clothing-chain-dies-in-accident-7249612%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Isak%20Andic%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Spanish%20clothing%20retailer%20Mango%2C%20one%20of%20Europe's%20largest%20fashion%20groups%2C%20with