%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Famit-shah-one-nation-one-election-agenda-aaj-tak-bjp-parliament-session-2649951-2024-12-14%3Futm_source%3DStory_hp%26utm_medium%3DStory%26utm_campaign%3Dhome_Story%5C%22%3EAgenda%20Aaj%20Tak%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister's%20comments%20come%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20volley%20against%20the%20Congress%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20accused%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Btraitor%26quot%3B%20and%20part%20of%20a%20dangerous%20triangle%20-%20including%20%26quot%3Bsome%20agencies%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20and%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%20-%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20destabilise%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20followed%20a%20report%20by%20French%20outlet%20Mediapart%20that%20claimed%20%26quot%3Bhidden%20links%20between%20a%20giant%20of%20investigative%20journalism%20-%20a%20reference%20to%20OCCRP%20(the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%2C%20an%20Amsterdam-based%20news%20network)%20-%20and%20the%20US%20government%26quot%3B.%20Mediapart%20said%20the%20OCCRP%20is%20financially%20dependent%20on%20the%20United%20States%20and%20is%20also%20funded%20by%20George%20Soros'%20Open%20Foundation%20and%20countries%20like%20France%20and%20Sweden.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20said%20the%20OCCRP%20has%20published%20news%20reports%20targeting%20India%20which%20are%20then%20used%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20question%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20denied%20these%20claims%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Boutrageous%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734201480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fhfcgdq4g_amit-shah-pti_625x300_03_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsource-of-inspiration-abroad-amit-shahs-swipe-at-rahul-gandhi-7249942%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Attacking%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20%26quot%3Bsource%20of%20inspiration%26quot%3B%20for%20raising%20issues%20is%20abroad%20and%20he%20comes%20up%20with%20a%20new%20charge%20every%20time%20a%20Parliament%20session%20is%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsource-of-inspiration-abroad-amit-shahs-swipe-at-rahul-gandhi-7249942%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThose%20Who%20Speak%20Truth...%26quot%3B%3A%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20On%20High%20Court%20Judge's%20Remarks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20on%20Saturday%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Opposition%20for%20initiating%20impeachment%20notices%20against%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20and%20Allahabad%20High%20Court's%20Justice%20Shekhar%20Kumar%20Yadav%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bwhoever%20speaks%20the%20truth%26quot%3B%20is%20threatened%20in%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20World%20Hindu%20Economic%20Forum%202024%2C%20he%20also%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20practicing%20double%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20speaks%20the%20truth%2C%20these%20people%20will%20pressurise%20him%20with%20impeachment%20(motions)%2C%20and%20still%20they%20talk%20about%20the%20Constitution.%20Look%20at%20their%20double%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20judge%20said%20there%20should%20be%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20and%20the%20world%20over%20the%20feelings%20of%20the%20majority%20community%20are%20respected%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UP%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20a%20person's%20crime%20if%20he%20voices%20these%20opinions%2C%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShouldn't%20there%20be%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20in%20the%20country%3F%20The%20world%20over%2C%20the%20system%20runs%20as%20per%20what%20the%20majority%20community%20says%20and%20India%20is%20saying%20the%20discrimination%20between%20majority%20and%20minority%20community%20should%20end.%20They%20(the%20Congress)%20will%20pressurize%2C%20because%20it%20is%20their%20old%20habit%20of%20strangulating%20the%20Constitution%20and%20managing%20the%20system%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Adityanath%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20the%20notice%20to%20impeach%20Dhankhar%20for%20his%20alleged%20partisan%20role%20as%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%20the%20Vice%20President%20is%20doing%20his%20duty%20as%20presiding%20officer%20of%20the%20Upper%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Opposition%20is%20worried%20as%20to%20how%20a%20farmer's%20son%20has%20reached%20this%20position.%20If%20someone%20as%20a%20judge%20as%20well%20as%20a%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%20puts%20forth%20truth%20on%20a%20social%20and%20cultural%20platform%2C%20he%20is%20threatened%20with%20impeachment%2C%26quot%3B%20Adityanath%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20several%20opposition%20parties%20on%20Friday%20moved%20a%20notice%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20the%20impeachment%20of%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20Judge%20Shekhar%20Kumar%20Yadav%20over%20his%20alleged%20controversial%20remarks%20at%20a%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20event%20on%20December%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20sought%20details%20pertaining%20to%20the%20controversy%20from%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20the%20society%20and%20country%20need%20to%20expose%20those%20who%20want%20to%20suppress%20the%20truth.%20Those%20who%20spurn%20India's%20legacy%20should%20be%20exposed%2C%20he%20said%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20Opposition%20says%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20never%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sanatan%20religion%20never%20claimed%20it%20is%20great%2C%20or%20it%20never%20said%20its%20supremacy%20must%20be%20accepted%2C%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20neither%20controlled%20anyone%20with%20a%20sword%20nor%20did%20it%20stake%20a%20claim%20on%20anyone's%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20PM%20Modi%20showering%20flowers%20on%20workers%20who%20built%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20for%20their%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20there%20will%20also%20be%20rulers%20who%20chopped%20the%20hands%20of%20workers%20who%20built%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20cannot%20establish%20itself%20as%20a%20strong%20economy%20by%20forgetting%20its%20legacy%2C%20the%20UP%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20economy%20stood%20at%2010th%20or%2011th%20position%20after%2070%20years%2C%20but%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20made%20it%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20in%2010%20years%2C%20and%20in%202027%20India%20will%20be%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20is%20now%20the%20country's%20second%20largest%20economy%20and%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20grow%20to%20USD%201%20trillion%2C%20Adityanath%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734200640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fv7rs1pj_up-chief-minister-yogi-adityanath_625x300_28_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-who-speak-truth-yogi-adityanath-on-allahabad-high-court-judges-remarks-7249862%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adit