fter%20a%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20first%20sitting%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elected%20in%202024%20has%20already%20taken%20place%2C%20the%20earliest%20appointed%20date%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20that%20can%20only%20be%20notified%20is%20the%20first%20sitting%20of%20the%20House%20elected%20in%20the%202029%20elections.%20This%20means%20that%20simultaneous%20polls%20could%20be%20held%20by%202034%20when%20the%20full%20term%20of%20that%20House%20ends%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20told%20NDTV%2C%20explaining%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734199260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F78c91mcc_lok-sabha-generic-ians_625x300_06_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-amend-j-k-reorganisation-act-2019-to-align-it-with-one-nation-one-poll-initiative-7249786%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20will%20introduce%20a%20bill%20to%20amend%20'The%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%202019'%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20next%20week%2C%20to%20integrate%20the%20Union%20Territory%20with%20its%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20initiative%2C%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-amend-j-k-reorganisation-act-2019-to-align-it-with-one-nation-one-poll-initiative-7249786%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98No%20Good%20Deed%E2%80%99%20Creator%20on%20Fiery%20Season%20Finale%20Twists%2C%20Season%202%20Plans%20and%20Why%20%5BSPOILER%5D%20Originally%20Won%20the%20House%20on%20Derby%20Drive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734199200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNoGoodDeed-MAIN.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236246431%2