.businessinsider.com%2Fgmail-voice-note-email-pitching-for-work-freelancer-voice-memo-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20voice%20notes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20keeping%20each%20other%20updated%20on%20our%20daily%20lives.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20would%20rant%20to%20him%20if%20I%20had%20a%20bad%20day%20at%20work%2C%20and%20he%20was%20always%20there%20to%20listen%20and%20validate%20my%20emotions.%20He'd%20tell%20me%20about%20his%20family%2C%20his%20dog%2C%20and%20his%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20never%20in%20my%20wildest%20dreams%20did%20I%20imagine%20he%20would%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-learned-breakups-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20break%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20me%20via%20voice%20note%20while%20I%20was%20on%20a%20work%20trip%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4a00f55-c57e-4997-b653-f023f046e358%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20had%20gotten%20into%20a%20fight%20right%20before%20my%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expressed%20that%20I%20didn't%20like%20it%20when%20he%20had%20no%20plan%20for%20our%20dates%20in%20advance.%20We%20started%20bickering%20about%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-doux-ceo-mom-five-boys-gender-roles-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20gender%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20relationships%2C%20and%20then%20our%20fight%20escalated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20angry%20that%20we%20were%20bickering%20over%20something%20in%20texts%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20an%20in-person%20conversation%20and%20was%20only%20getting%20worse.%20But%20at%20no%20point%20did%20I%20think%20something%20so%20silly%20could%20lead%20us%20to%20call%20things%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20good%20to%20spend%2010%20days%20apart.%20I%20traveled%20to%20Tbilisi%2C%20Georgia%2C%20for%20work%2C%20which%20was%20a%20seven-hour%20flight%20away%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20five%20days%20later%2C%20during%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20send%20a%20voice%20note%2C%20apologizing.%20I'm%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-an-only-child-but-only-one-expected-have-kids-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20child%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20as%20a%20kid%2C%20whenever%20my%20needs%20were%20unmet%20by%20my%20emotionally%20unavailable%20parents%2C%20my%20coping%20mechanism%20was%20to%20throw%20a%20tantrum%20to%20get%20them%20to%20notice%20my%20needs.%20Hence%2C%20when%20I%20felt%20like%20he%20wasn't%20meeting%20my%20needs%2C%20I%20bull-dozed%20into%20complaining%20rather%20than%20healthily%20addressing%20it.%20He%20sent%20a%20voice%20note%20back%2C%20breaking%20up%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20was%20confusing%20and%20painful.%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20it%20was%20real.%20I%20cried%20for%20two%20weeks%20straight%20after%20the%20breakup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22556d57b2-444b-435b-a5ed-8ca98137c01b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20pain%20still%20haunts%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20out%20I%20was%20single%20again%20via%20a%20voice%20note%20was%20hard.%20I%20understand%20that%20no%20one%20really%20owes%20anyone%20anything%20for%20just%20two%20months%20of%20dating%2C%20but%20I%20still%20feel%20like%20I%20deserved%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F10-second-communication-hack-prepare-3-topics-supercommunicator-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eface-to-face%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20felt%20like%20my%20feelings%20didn't%20matter%20in%20this%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I'm%20proud%20of%20myself%20because%20I%20was%20vulnerable%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20especially%20during%20those%20breakup%20voice%20note%20exchanges.%20Before%20that%2C%20I%20was%20always%20playing%20the%20chill%2C%20cool%20girl%20who%20just%20didn't%20care%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20hold%20the%20power.%20I%20am%20also%20proud%20that%20I%20didn't%20try%20to%20get%20him%20to%20