%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProduction%20said%20I'd%20need%20to%20be%20on%20set%20from%2010%3A30%20a.m.%20to%204%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20and%20this%20would%20be%20an%20outdoor%20event%20requiring%20me%20to%20stand%20and%20walk%20during%20service.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELastly%2C%20I%20was%20advised%20that%20this%20would%20be%20a%20seafood-focused%20challenge%2C%20and%20chefs%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20accommodate%20any%20allergies%20or%20dietary%20restrictions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20night%20before%20the%20big%20day%2C%20I%20received%20a%20call%20sheet%20with%20more%20specific%20directions%20to%20the%20filming%20location.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%2C%20my%20credentials%20were%20checked%20before%20I%20was%20let%20onto%20the%20set.%20The%20production%20team%20had%20me%20sign%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ea%20non-disclosure%20agreement%20(NDA)%3Cspan%3E%2C%20then%20briefed%20me%20on%20more%20details%20of%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258b39930-b232-4a06-925d-b51f0762fcd7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20I%20was%20on%20set%2C%20though%2C%20filming%20felt%20somewhat%20laid-back%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20contestants%20cooked%2C%20we%20could%20get%20drinks%20from%20the%20on-set%20bar.%20We%20were%20also%20able%20to%20get%20name-brand%20snacks%20and%20beverages%20from%20production's%20craft%20services%20but%20were%20told%20to%20keep%20those%20off%20of%20the%20set.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20production%20crew%20also%20reminded%20us%20to%20mingle%20and%20keep%20our%20phones%20away%20to%20help%20create%20a%20buzzy%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229620505f-8380-47f4-9cd6-509a4fa043c2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EContestants%20staggered%20the%20start%20times%20of%20their%20cooks%20so%20food%20was%20served%20hot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20preparing%20vegetables%20outside%20on%20%26quot%3BTo