Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224898%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Holiday%20shopping%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67352519fa0140cdd5633ce8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223254%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EConsumer%20sentiment%20and%20spending%20will%20remain%20strong%20in%202025%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnalysts%20expect%20discretionary%20cash%20flow%20for%20US%20consumers%20to%20grow%205.2%25%20compared%20to%20a%204.4%25%20rise%20in%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20strength%20will%20lead%20to%20outsize%20gains%20among%20discretionary%20stocks%2C%20with%20some%20outperformance%20in%20staples%2C%20too%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer%20spending%20will%20be%20solid%20again%20next%20year%2C%20boosting%20stocks%20in%20discretionary%20sectors%20as%20well%20as%20consumer%20staples%2C%20according%20to%20analysts%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20expects%20discretionary%20cash%20flow%20for%20US%20consumers%20to%20pick%20up%20in%202025%2C%20growing%205.2%25%20compared%20to%20a%204.4%25%20rise%20in%202024%2C%20helped%20by%20more%20reasonable%20inflation%20levels%20and%20falling%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20robust%20cash%20flows%20will%20support%20a%20healthy%20discretionary%20spending%20backdrop%20and%20higher%20savings%20for%20US%20consumers%2C%20though%20disposable%20income%20will%20grow%20slightly%20slower%20than%20in%202024%2C%20down%20to%204.9%25%20from%205.8%25%2C%20though%20still%20robust%20given%20historical%20levels%2C%20the%20firm%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAggregate%20household%20balance%20sheets%20remain%20robust%2C%20with%20net%20worth%20to%20DPI%20and%20household%20home%20equity%20as%20a%20share%20of%20GDP%20near%20all-time%20highs%2C%20which%20along%20with%20encouraging%20signs%20in%20consumer%20confidence%20should%20support%20a%20resilient%20spending%20backdrop%20despite%20supporting%20a%20modestly%20higher%20savings%20rate%20for%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20added%20that%20there%20are%20signs%20of%20improving%20consumer%20sentiment%20more%20generally.%20The%20firms'%202024%20holiday%20survey%20found%20that%20lower-income%20consumers%20plan%20to%20spend%20more%20this%20year%2C%20while%20perceptions%20of%20prices%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20promotions%20moderated%20from%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20sustained%20healthy%20outlook%20for%20consumers%2C%20a%20few%20corners%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20are%20poised%20for%20strong%20gains%2C%20the%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20sees%20the%20most%20upside%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-best-sectors-utilities-tech-trump-trade-ubs-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscretionary%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20sector%20will%20likely%20continue%20to%20outperform%20the%20more%20defensive%20consumer%20staples%20sector%20as%20bullishness%20continues%20to%20soar.%20However%2C%20consumer%20staples%20will%20also%20enjoy%20some%20tailwinds%20going%20into%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20a%20rotation%20away%20from%20Staples%20(given%20its%20defensive%20nature)%20to%20Discretionary%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months%20as%20the%20market's%20assessment%20of%20recession%20risk%20fell%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20this%20to%20continue%20in%202025%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20said%20discretionary%20stocks%20are%20poised%20for%20growth%20amid%20easing%20interest%20rates%20and%20as%20their%20share%20of%20consumers'%20wallets%20normalizes%2C%20particularly%20among%20stocks%20like%20Target%2C%20Bath%20%26amp%3B%20Body%20Works%2C%20and%20DICK'S%20Sporting%20Goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20shares%20of%20consumer%20sector%20companies%20like%20Walmart%2C%20with%20healthy%20supply%20chain%20investments%20and%20long-term%20drivers%20like%20growth%20in%20alternative%20revenue%20streams%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20outperform.%20The%20retailer's%20stock%20is%20up%20around%2078%25%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20names%20seeing%20greater%20competition%20and%20higher%20risks%20related%20to%20tariffs%2C%20though%2C%20will%20likely%20see%20a%20tougher%20environment%20in%202025%2C%20the%20bank%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20companies%20including%20Autozone%20and%20RH%20(formerly%20Restoration%20Hardware).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20said%20defensive%20sectors%20like%20consumer%20staples%20also%20have%20an%20improving%20setup%20as%20consumer%20sentiment%20rises.%20The%20sector%20saw%20inflows%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summer%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Finvestors-consumer-staples-economic-slowdown-defensive-stocks-recession-stock-market-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecession%20fears%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0spiked%2C%20but%20it%20has%20since%20seen%20losses%20amid%20stronger%20bullish%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20emerging%20tailwinds%20as%20volume%2Fmix%20continues%20to%20improve%20amid%20a%20constructive%20consumer%20backdrop%2C%20and%20pricing%20could%20return%20as%20a%20top%20line%20lever%20for%20some%20given%20a%20reacceleration%20in%20input%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20they%20see%20continued%20momentum%20from%20market%20share%20gainers%20like%20Philip%20Morris%20and%20Monster%20Beverage%20Corporation.%20They%20warned%2C%20though%2C%20that%20companies%20with%20increasing%20competition%20from%20private%20labels%20and%20eroding%20returns%20on%20promotions%E2%80%94like%20Kraft%20Heinz%2C%20Hershey%20and%20Clorox%E2%80%94warrant%20more%20caution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid