E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndira%20and%20her%20team%20screened%20%3Cem%3EPutul%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20the%20prestigious%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMarch%C3%A9%20du%20Film%20%3C%2Fem%3E(or%20Cannes%20Film%20Market).%20Though%20the%20film%20was%20screened%20out%20of%20competition%2C%20the%20response%20was%20moving.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20emotionally%20overwhelmed%20and%20cried%20when%20I%20turned%20back%20to%20see%20the%20audience%20appreciating%20the%20film.%20Many%20international%20filmmakers%20and%20scriptwriters%20approached%20me%20to%20discuss%20it%2C%20as%20they%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Indira.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-500x889.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indira%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20March%C3%A9%20du%20Film%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-500x889.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-169x300.jpg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433-150x267.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-2_11zon-1733816433.jpg%20620w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388047%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIndira%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20March%C3%A9%20du%20Film%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPutul%20is%20a%20home-grown%20film%20with%20no%20foreign%20collaboration%2C%20and%20receiving%20a%20standing%20ovation%20during%20its%20screening%20in%20a%20mid-sized%20theatre%