20cultural%20constraints%20involved%20in%20menstrual%20practices.%20I%20myself%20used%20cloths%20during%20my%20adolescence.%20But%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20we%20should%20accept%20this%20situation.%20We%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381663%2Fmenstrual-education-prazna-foundation-jaipur-project-kishori-women-health-period-shame%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emust%20raise%20awareness.%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rituporna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlima%20shares%20an%20incident%20when%20a%20male%20gynaecologist%20came%20to%20take%20the%20session.%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20were%20open%20to%20discussing%20their%20issues%20and%20actively%20participated%20in%20the%20learning%20process.%20In%20a%20scenario%20where%20women%20were%20reluctant%20to%20speak%20about%20periods%20to%20their%20male%20family%20members%2C%20this%20is%20an%20achievement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alima%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(SEED)%20were%20the%20ones%20who%20first%20taught%20us%20what%20sanitary%20napkins%20are%2C%20why%20they%20are%20used%2C%20and%20what%20are%20the%20benefits%20of%20using%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20reflects%20Soma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20session%20ends%20with%20distributing%20two%20sanitary%20pad%20packets%2C%20enough%20to%20cover%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20needs%20for%20an%20entire%20menstrual%20cycle.%20The%20gesture%20is%20not%20just%20practical%20but%20symbolic%2C%20representing%20a%20shift%20in%20how%20women%20perceive%20their%20own%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20almost%20every%20woman%20uses%20sanitary%20napkins%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soma%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Amphan%20and%20Aila%20%5Bcyclones%5D%20happened%2C%20we%20were%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20trouble.%20Those%20were%20terrible%20times.%20People%20in%20Sagar%20Island%20suffer%20from%20poverty%20and%20do%20not%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20buy%20sanitary%20napkins.%20During%20the%20cyclone%2C%20our%20condition%20worsened