%20and%20eventually%20collaborating%20with%20Ultraviolette%20Automotive%20on%20special%20projects%20where%20I%20was%20working.%E2%80%9D%20Narayan%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20philosophy%20prioritising%20passion%20over%20academic%20qualifications%2C%20encouraged%20Jijo%E2%80%99s%20creativity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhotographing%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20F77%20Mach%202%20motorcycle%20showcased%20Jijo%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20capture%20moments%20with%20enthusiasm.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20my%20pictures%20to%20show%20the%20excitement%20of%20the%20launch%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jijo%20says%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Ultraviolette%2C%20we%20believe%20diversity%20in%20talent%20and%20perspective%20drives%20us%20forward%2C%20and%20Jijo%20is%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20this.%20His%20dedication%20and%20commitment%20remind%20us%20of%20resilience%20and%20determination.%20We%E2%80%99re%20proud%20to%20have%20him%20as%20a%20valued%20member%20of%20our%20Ultraviolette%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20Narayan%20shares.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20a%20rockstar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20World%20Down%20Syndrome%20Day%202023%2C%20the%20campaign%20%E2%80%98With%20Us%20Not%20For%20Us%E2%80%99%20featured%20Ultraviolette%20Automotive%E2%80%99s%20video%20about%20Jijo%20to%20show%20what%20a%20truly%20inclusive%20workplace%20looks%20like.%20He%20was%20also%20featured%20in%20%3Cem%3EEnable%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EUK%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESome%20Good%20News%20Australia%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJijo%20is%20expanding%20his%20art%20by%20also%20learning%20music%20along%20with%20Hum-Drum%20Drumming%20Classes%20with%20Rzhude%20David.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20a%20rockstar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20declares%20with%20a%20confident%20smile%2C%20reflecting%20the%20positive%20attitude%20that%20fuels%20his%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C