%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F382844%2Fgrow-avocado-indoors-guide-small-space-home-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20indoor%20plants%20%3C%2Fa%3Egenerally%20need%20less%20water%20because%20their%20growth%20slows%20down.%20The%20cooler%20temperatures%20and%20reduced%20sunlight%20also%20mean%20that%20the%20soil%20takes%20longer%20to%20dry%20out%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20overwatering.%20Overwatered%20plants%20are%20more%20prone%20to%20root%20rot%20and%20fungal%20infections%2C%20which%20can%20damage%20the%20plant%20permanently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20overwatering%2C%20check%20the%20moisture%20level%20of%20the%20soil%20before%20watering.%20Stick%20your%20finger%20about%20an%20inch%20into%20the%20soil%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20feels%20dry%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20water.%20If%20it%20still%20feels%20moist%2C%20wait%20a%20few%20more%20days%20before%20checking%20again.%20For%20plants%20like%20succulents%20or%20cacti%2C%20which%20are%20more%20drought-tolerant%2C%20water%20even%20less%20frequently%20during%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Provide%20adequate%20light%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReduced%20daylight%20during%20the%20winter%20months%20can%20be%20tough%20on%20indoor%20plants%2C%20especially%20those%20that%20require%20bright%2C%20direct%20sunlight%20like%20money%20plant%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360100%2Faloe-vera-farming-products-satara-farmer-hrushikesh-jayasing-dhane-earn-crores-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealoe%20vera%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20spider%20plant.%20Without%20enough%20light%2C%20they%20can%20become%20leggy%2C%20and%20weak%2C%20and%20stop%20producing%20new%20leaves%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202725px)%20100vw%2