er%20the%20secret%20behind%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20exquisite%20taste%2C%20some%20say%20it%20lies%20in%20the%20cream%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20come%20specially%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345649%2Fhistory-of-parsi-dairy-farm-mumbai-nariman-ardeshir-legacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20dairy%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Ashram%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Aslam%20Butter%20Chicken%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Delhi%20touts%20its%20recipe%20of%20butter%20chicken%20as%20a%20simple%20one%2C%20Aslam%20Butter%20Chicken%2C%20which%20has%20been%20doling%20out%20the%20delicacy%20for%2025%20years%20now%2C%20strays%20away%20from%20this%20levity.%20Secret%20%3Cem%3Emasalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20roasted%20and%20charcoal-grilled%20chicken%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20butter%20go%20into%20the%20recipe%20at%20Aslam%E2%80%99s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FwgycX7iscXg%3Fsi%3DdMq2Yp_isBLuq2OB%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recipe%20is%20a%20well-guarded%20secret%20that%20is%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20generations%20of%20the%20family.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20Aslam%20learnt%20it%20from%20his%20father%20and%20grandfather%3B%20till%20date%2C%20this%20consistency%20reflects%20in%20the%20dish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cntraveller.in%2Fstory%2Fbest-butter-chicken-in-new-delhi-as-picked-by-the-citys-foodies-moti-mahal-gulatis-pandararo