nce%20of%20tree%20plantation.%20By%20planting%20more%20trees%2C%20we%20ensured%20that%20water%20was%20stored%20underground%2C%20which%20helped%20maintain%20a%20supply%20even%20during%20droughts.%20Trees%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20absorbing%20and%20conserving%20water%2C%20offering%20a%20lifeline%20in%20dry%20seasons%20by%20using%20moisture%20efficiently%20and%20sustaining%20the%20land%20and%20the%20community.%20In%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20we%20have%20planted%20approximately%201%2C27%2C000%20trees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201599px)%20100vw%2C%201599px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-10.20.32-1-1-1733488195.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20Abhay%20has%20planted%20approximately%201%2C27%2C000%20trees%20in%20different%20villages%20in%20Satara%20district%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-10.20.32-1-1-1733488195.jpeg%201599w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-10.20.32-1-1-1733488195-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-10.20.32-1-1-1733488195-500x225.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-10.20.32-1-1-1733488195-768x346.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-10.20.32-1-1-1733488195-1536x692.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-10.20.32-1-1-1733488195-1200x540.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-